/pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouselaboratory.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2361.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Poison Making From 200-250 </span><hr size=1> Well since i just finished this off i figure i would post and let you know how it all whent.. <br><br>I used the Spirit of Shoth (or how ever thats spelt) to raise my skill. I when from 200-250 in about ... 4 hours. <br><br>Now keep im mind i did this with 90 Wisdom, 88 Charisma and 219 Dex. I did start with a 75ish Wisdom and that made CONSIDERABLE diference in how many combines=skill ups i would get so it a MUST to have hight int-wis. <br><br>I started out with 4.5 K.. I then followed the recipe and bought 2 stacks of Vials 2 stacks of Constriction- 4 stacks of Creepy Ive.  <br>I would combine till all the constriction ran out then sell these back. On an avarage i was getting 1 to 2 silver more every time which of course added up after a while.<br>I think the total price was around 11pp per combine .. and i was selling them for 14pp back so its a good 2pp or so profit per poison. Now of course you will burn some when you start but towards the end you are actuly making back some of that pp. <br><br>When i was finished i had poison making 250 and 3899pp meaning i really only spent a little over 6oopp from 200 to 250 which is SUPER cheaper then working with stanos :)  <br><br> Well there you go my 2 coppers :P  <br><br><center><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=138165> Neijek Domisilva </a><br>Beloved of Velondra Domisilva<br>Proud Assasin of Bristlebane<br>Grandmaster Toxiologist for Phoenix Crusaders </center><br> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uneijek.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Neijek</A> at: 7/23/02 11:16:46 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uvaslin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vaslin</A></sp